                    </div>
                <div class="row mt-3">
                   Specialized diabetes treatment services:
                   <br/><br/>
                    <ul >
                        <li>Comprehensive diabetes management for adults (Type 1 and 2 diabetes care)</li>
                        <li>Antenatal diabetes (diabetes in pregnancy) care</li>
                        <li>Assessment and treatment of associated complications of diabetes such as neuropathy, nephropathy and retinopathy</li>
                        <li>Specialized lab tests (C-peptide, anti-GAD, TSH receptor antibodies, Chromogranin, IGF 1, IGFBP3)</li>
                        <li>Dynamic endocrine tests, ACTH stimulation tests, glucose tolerance test, dexamethasone suppression test and water deprivation test</li>
                        <li>Continuous Glucose Monitoring (CGM) using Ipro 2 CGM device</li>
                        <li>Insulin pump therapy</li>
                        <li>Assessment of diabetic retinopathy</li>
                        <li>Treatment for associated diseases such as hypercholesterolaemia &nbsp;and hypertension</li>
                    </ul>
                  
                    The Endocrinology Department of Caritas Hospital also provides treatment for:
                    <br/><br/>
                        <ul >
                            <li>Thyroid disorders</li>
                            <li>Metabolic bone disease</li>
                            <li>Obesity / overweight(including bariatric management and surgery)</li>
                            <li>Sexual disorders</li>
